{
  "texts": [
    "We also contribute to their knowledge growth by developing an online version that, thanks to the robust GPT4-LM database, provides additional contextualized information, tips, and recommendations on how operators can better troubleshoot, understand, or care for their factory.",
    "To preserve the ecosystem, we also include the maximum pollution rate as a parameter that should always be low for production.",
    "Through various prompts and responses using the GPT chatbots, operators can receive accurate and helpful information about production status.",
    "We also incorporate faulty equipment discovery and root cause analysis to ease troubleshooting and a synthetic data generation feature for data augmentation needs.For future works, we intend to include image and sound recognition features in the industrial GPT chatbots to ease troubleshooting tasks.",
    "We also plan to incorporate our GPT chatbots into existing legacy devices in factories, such as PLCs and SCADA systems, to empower their functionalities.Fig. 22Fig."
  ]
}